====Last Comic Standing==== Phan was the original winner of ''[[Last Comic Standing]]''<ref name="NCTimes" /><ref name="AsianWeek" /> and won in the finals against [[Ralphie May]] in 2003. In Fall 2004, he returned for the third season dubbed "Battle of the Best" which was season 1 against season 2. In the fifth round, he and May got eliminated and contestant [[Dave Mordal]] who would become the runner-up stayed in. The Season 2 elimination results had winner and future third placeman [[John Heffron]] staying in and [[Kathleen Madigan]] and [[Jay London]] eliminated.
